data.title: Some Descendants of the ANJOU Family Related to George Washington 1st US President
data.text:
4. i. Geoffrey I 'Grisegnelle' D' ANJOU 2 795 1869 was born 11 Nov 0938 in Anjou, Pays-de-la-Loire, France 2 and died 21 Jul 0987 in Killed in Siege of Marcon, near Ch√¢teau-du-Loir, France.2 1869 9. i. William III 'Taillifer' DE TOULOUSE Comte de Toulouse, Albi & Quercy was born Cir 0975 in Toulouse, Haute-Garonne, Midi-Pyrenees, France and died in Sep 1037 of Toulouse, Haute-Garonne, Midi-Pyrenees, France. 11. ii. Constance DE PROVENCE 1633 1881 1882 was born Cir 0986 in Toulouse, Haute-Garonne, Midi-Pyrenees, France,1882 died 25 Jul 1032 in Meulan, Yvelines, Ile-de-France, France,1883 and was buried in St. Denis Basilica, Paris, Ile-de-France, France. 15. i. Pons III DE TOULOUSE Comte de Toulouse, Albi & Dijon 1715 was born Abt 0990 in Prob Toulouse, Haute-Garonne, Midi-Pyrenees, France 1715 and died about 1060 in St. Sernin, Toulouse, France.1715

16. i. Advisa 'Capet' DE FRANCE Princess of France, Comtesse D'Auxerre 68 1615 was born about 1003 of Auxerre, Yonne, Bourgogne, France 68 1615 and died after 5 Jun 1063 of Nevers, Nievre, Bourgogne, France.68 1615 17. ii. Henry I 'Capet' DE FRANCE King of France [1031-1060] was born about 1006 in Reims, Marne, Champagne, France,584 1887 died 2 Aug 1060 in Vitry-aux-Loges, Loiret, Orleanais/Centre, France 584 1279 1444 about age 54, and was buried in St. Denis Basilica, Paris, Ile-de-France, France. 18. iii. Adela 'Capet' DE FRANCE Princess of France, Comtesse de Flanders 1626 1840 1841 1846 1847 1848 was born about 1009 in Auxerre, Yonne, Bourgogne, France 1841 and died 5 Jun 1063 in Monastere De L'o, Messines, France 1840 1846 about age 54. 19. iv. Robert 'the Old' 'Capet' DE BURGUNDY Duc de Bourgogne [1032-1076] was born circa 1010 in Meulan, Yvelines, Ile-de-France, France 1888 and died 21 Mar 1076 in Fleury-sur-Ouche, Cote-d'Or, Bourgogne, France 1888 at age 66. 21. i. Hildegarde Of BURGUNDY 2 68 was born about 1050 in Dijon, Cote d'Or, Bourgogne, France 2 68 and died after 1104.68

22. i. William IV DE TOULOUSE Comte de Toulouse, Duc de Narbonne 68 1715 was born about 1040 in Huesca, Spain 68 1715 and died about 1093 in Died while on crusade to the Holy Land 68 1715 about age 53.

23. i. Phillip I 'the Fair' CAPET King of France [1060-1108] was born before 23 May 1052 in Reims, Marne, Champagne, France,584 1532 died 29 Jul 1108 in Meulan, Yvelines, Ile-de-France, France,584 1444 1532 1533 and was buried in Abbaye St-Benoit-sur-Loire, Loiret, Orleanais/Centre, France. 24. ii. Hugh 'le Magnus' CAPET Duc de Bourgogne, Comte de Vermandois was born about 1057 in Vermandois, Aisne, Picardy, France,1704 died 18 Oct 1101 in Tarsus, Cilicie (from wounds at Battle of Heraclea) 1702 1705 about age 44, and was buried in Cathedral of St. Paul de Tarse, Turkey.

25. i. Matilda 'Maud' Of FLANDERS 1684 1831 1832 was born in 1032 in Flanders (now Belgium), Nord, France, died 3 Nov 1083 in Caen, Calvados, Normandy, France at age 51, and was buried in Church of Holy Trinity, Caen, Calvados, France. 26. ii. Robert I LE FRISON Comte De Flanders was born about 1035 in Flanders (now Belgium), Nord, France and died 13 Oct 1093 in Kassel, Hessen-Nassau, Prussia about age 58. 27. iii. Baldwin I DE HAINAULT Count d'Hainault 1895 1896 1897 1898 1899 1900 was born about 1030 in Hainault, Flanders, France (now Belgium), died 7 Jul 1070 in Hainault, Flanders, France (now Belgium) about age 40, and was buried in Abbey of Hasnon, Belgium.

28. i. Henry I DE BURGUNDY 2 was born about 1035 in Dijon, Cote d'Or, Bourgogne, France 2 and died 27 Jan 1074 of Bourgogne, France 2 about age 39. Henry married Sybile DE BARCELONA,2 daughter of Berenguer I Ramon 'el curvo' DE BARCELONA Conde de Barcelona and Gisla DE LLUCA, about 1056.2 Sybile was born about 1035 in Barcelona, Catalonia, Spain 2 and died after 6 Jul 1074 of Bourgogne, France.2
